data.description: GORGEOUS ELEGANT Residence!!  Rare Find!   Situated on a 1/3 acre corner lot in Establish Neighborhood on McColl Rd just south of Business 83 in McAllen.  Fantastic place to entertain! Gorgeous kitchen with Granite Countertops, and Terrazzo Tile. This custom home offers plenty of room for a growing family. It  features 5 Bedrooms, 4 Baths, 2-1/2 baths. 4,450 sq ft. 3 large separated living areas including one, atrium-style room in the center of the home with 2 story ceiling, skylights, and large stone fireplace. The kitchen feature stainless still appliances (all included) and beautiful granite counter tops.  Each Bedroom has its own bathroom, and the bonus room could be maid's quarters which also has a full bath! Upstairs is a fantastic study/gallery and the 5th bedroom w/ 1/2 bath.  Front exterior entrance features a beautiful cantera stone water fountain.  One Mile to Expressway 83 (Interstate 2) Easy Access to 2nd Street Trails.  Close  to shopping/medical centers, restaurants.
